              PTD™
            </div>

            <div class="transform translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-300">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2 uppercase tracking-tighter">PAY THE DØLLS™</h2>
              <p class="text-xs font-mono opacity-70 mb-4 group-hover:opacity-90">Cultural Commerce Platform</p>
